(241, 1, '2018-02-16 07:53:38', '2018-02-16 07:53:38', 'MBBS, Diploma in Otorhinolaryngology (DLO), MD (General Medicine)\r\nDr. Arun R Vadavi is a General Physician & a Diabetologist. He practices at Apollo Hospitals in Bannerghatta Road, Bangalore. He has been involved in various training activities and has been a trainer at the Johns Hopkins Academy and American Academy of CME for certified courses in India. He is a post graduate teacher in Diabetology at the Rajiv Gandhi Health University.\r\n\r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Management.</li>\r\n	<li>Type 1 Diabetes.</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin therapy.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypothyroidism.</li>\r\n	<li>Hyperthyroidism.</li>\r\n	<li>Pituitary Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Pediatric Endocrine Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Ultrasound.</li>', 'pasha', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '164-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-16 07:53:38', '2018-02-16 07:53:38', '', 164, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/164-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(242, 1, '2018-02-16 09:46:34', '2018-02-16 09:46:34', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine), FIDM, FEM\r\n\r\nDr. Arshad Punjani is an Internal Medicine and Diabetologist in Hyderguda, Hyderabad and has an experience of 18 years in these fields. He completed MBBS from Dr NTR University of health sciences in 2007 and MD – Internal Medicine from Dr NTR University of health sciences in 2008. Some of the services provided by the doctor are: Thyroid Disorders, Anemia, Asthma Fever, Consultant Physician and General Illness Diabetes etc.\r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n\r\nDiabetes Mellitus.\r\nType 1 Diabetes.\r\nInsulin Management.\r\nThyroid Disorders.\r\nHypertension.', 'Dr.Arshad Punjani', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-16 09:46:34', '2018-02-16 09:46:34', '', 36, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/36-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(245, 1, '2018-02-16 12:53:55', '2018-02-16 12:53:55', '\r\n<div class="diabetes-program">\r\n        <div class="content">\r\n          <div>\r\n             \r\n            <p>Are you having a hard time maintaining normal blood glucose levels despite medications? You might be at a risk of developing serious complications of diabetes! It’s time you need a comprehensive management to reduce the risk of complications and to attain normal blood sugar levels. Sugar 360 is an intensive year-long program that provides deep care in order to attain normal blood sugar levels consistently. The diabetes program includes:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>In-clinic consultations with diabetologists and endocrinologists with a treatment plan and Glucose Profile.</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;Periodical diagnostic tests and screening for diabetic complications and heart disease that include special tests for eye, kidney and heart.</li>\r\n<li>Technological assistance with Apollo Sugar app that provides reminders for follow-up exams, consultations and compliance with medications.</li>\r\n<li>Consultation with dietician for diet and exercise regimen.</li>\r\n<li>Frequent calls from the Diabetes Management for information, tips, and advice.</li>\r\n<li>Devices like glucometers and weighing machines for self-monitoring of blood glucose.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>With lifestyle consultations, periodical checkups, and monitoring, you are supported totally to manage your diabetes. Get proven outcomes in terms of HbA1c levels.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n            			      <figure class="entry-thumbnail"><img width="479" height="498" src="https://apollosugar.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Asset-3.png" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://apollosugar.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Asset-3.png 479w, https://apollosugar.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Asset-3-289x300.png 289w, https://apollosugar.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Asset-3-400x416.png 400w" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 479