(5334, 1, '2018-02-27 07:20:50', '2018-02-27 07:20:50', 'Gone are the days when people with diabetes couldn’t taste desserts at all. There are ways in which you can enjoy a few desserts &amp; still manage your diabetes well:\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5291" src="https://apollosugar.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Infographics_15-2-2018-1.png" alt="diabetes" width="930" height="1934" />\r\nSo, what are you waiting for? Try out some of these recipes &amp; you can thank us later! If you know some other amazing ways to enjoy desserts without affecting your diabetes control, do share them with us!', 'Trick your sweet tooth!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5290-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-27 07:20:50', '2018-02-27 07:20:50', '', 5290, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/5290-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
