le="text-align: justify;">Few patients may also associate with diabetes symptoms like experience extreme lethargy, agitation, and sometimes may also feel irritable without any reason.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The best thing if any individual sense the above said symptoms please do go to Apollo Sugar or any health care facility in out vicinity to take doctor advice.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a title="Apollo Sugar" href="http://www.apollosugar.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apollo sugar</a> is able to provide entire spectrum of diabetes services for effective diabetes management.</p>', 'Symptoms of Type 2 Diabetes', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2350-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-27 10:11:52', '2018-02-27 10:11:52', '', 2350, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/2350-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
