(354, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:24', '2017-06-17 07:03:24', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine), PGDD (Diabetology)\r\n\r\nDr. S.G.Moazam is a Diabetologist in Tolichowki, Hyderabad and has an experience of 17 years in this field. He completed MBBS from Al-Amin Medical College in 1995, MD - Internal Medicine from MRMC Gulburga in 2000 and Diploma in Diabetology from Horward University USA in 2008. He is a member of International Diabetes Federation (IDF) and European Association for the Study of Diabetes (EASD). Some of the services provided by the doctor are: Childhood Diabetes, Adult Diabetes, Type 1 Diabetes Treatment, Sugar Test and Insulin Treatment etc.\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Type 1 Diabetes.</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin Management.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '​Dr. S.G.Moazam', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', '%e2%80%8bdr-s-g-moazam', '', '', '2018-03-01 13:50:26', '2018-03-01 13:50:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=354', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
