(401, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:05', '2017-06-17 07:03:05', 'MBBS, AB Certified\r\nDr. Krishna Seshadri is an Endocrinologist and practices at Apollo Specialty Hospital in Vanagaram, Chennai. He is an American Board Certified Endocrinology Diabetes & Metabolism Senior Consultant. With several publications and numerous papers to his credit, he is a member of many organizations and an orator par excellence.\r\n\r\nHe provide treatment for:\r\n\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n	<li>Type 1 Diabetes.</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin Treatment.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypothyroidism.</li>\r\n	<li>Hyperthyroidism.</li>\r\n	<li>Pituitary Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Endocrine Disorders.</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Krishna G Seshadri', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-krishna-g-seshadri', '', '', '2018-03-01 13:39:13', '2018-03-01 13:39:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=401', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
