(377, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:14', '2017-06-17 07:03:14', 'Dr. Dwarakanath C.S. is a highly skilled doctor, having many years of experience in Endocriology. He has worked in many reputed hospitals of Bangalore and has over the years gained fame in this field. He is adept in Endocrinology and treats diabetes and related ailments. He has undergone GCP training in Investigator meetings. He has also participated in one Phase 3 trial in Type 2 Diabetes.', 'Dr. Dwarakanath C.S', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-dwarakanath-c-s', '', '', '2018-03-01 13:16:52', '2018-03-01 13:16:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=377', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(378, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:14', '2017-06-17 07:03:14', 'MBBS, Diploma in Otorhinolaryngology (DLO), MD (General Medicine) \r\nDr. Arun R Vadavi is a General Physician & a Diabetologist. He practices at Apollo Hospitals in Bannerghatta Road, Bangalore. He has been involved in various training activities and has been a trainer at the Johns Hopkins Academy and American Academy of CME for certified courses in India. He is a post graduate teacher in Diabetology at the Rajiv Gandhi Health University. \r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 and type 2).</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin therapy.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Complications.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Diet.</li>\r\n	<li>Cardiology.</li>\r\n	<li>Gestational Diabetes.</li>\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Arun R Vadavi', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-arun-r-vadavi', '', '', '2018-03-01 11:13:36', '2018-03-01 11:13:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=378', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(380, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:13', '2017-06-17 07:03:13', 'MBBS, MRCP (UK), FRCP (Endocrinology)\r\nDr. Santosh Shankar Narayan is a consultant Endocrinologist at Apollo Hospitals in Bannerghatta Road Bangalore. He had conducted extensive research in adult growth hormone deficiency, pituitary diseases, thyroid disorders, reproductive endocrinology, adrenal disorders, obesity, bone and metabolic disorders and parathyroid disorders. He also has expertise in treating people with diabetes, especially people who need insulin therapy.  \r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 and type 2).</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin Therapy.</li>\r\n	<li>Gestational Diabetes.</li>\r\n	<li>Endocrine Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Pituitary Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Parathyroid disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Goiter.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypertriglyceridemia</li>\r\n	<li>Hypertension.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypercholesterolemia.</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Santosh Shankar Narayan', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-santosh-shankar-narayan', '', '', '2018-03-01 13:14:41', '2018-03-01 13:14:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=380', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(381, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:13', '2017-06-17 07:03:13', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine), DM (Endocrinology)\r\nDr. Narendra B S, a Consultant Endocrinologist & Diabetologist, practices at Apollo Hospitals in Seshadripuram, Bangalore. \r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for: \r\n\r\n•	Diabetes.\r\n•	Type 1 Diabetes.\r\n•	Gestational Diabetes.\r\n•	Thyroid Disorders.\r\n•	Polycystic Ovarian Syndrome (PCOS).\r\n•	Pituitary/Adrenal Gland Disorders.\r\n•	Growth Disorders.\r\n•	HRT & Hormonal Disorders.\r\n•	Obesity.\r\n•	Menopause.\r\n•	Hirsutism.\r\n•	Erectile Dysfunction.\r\n', 'Dr. Narendra B S', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-narendra-b-s', '', '', '2018-03-01 13:12:14', '2018-03-01 13:12:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=381', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(383, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:12', '2017-06-17 07:03:12', 'MBBS, DNB (Internal Medicine), FICM  \r\nDr. Raghavendra Prakash practices at Apollo Specialty Hospital in Jayanagar 3 Block, Bangalore. He specializes in Internal Medicine, General Medicine, Diabetes, Thyroid disorders, gestational diabetes, rheumatic disorders, and intensive care medicine.  \r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes and Infectious Diseases.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Raghavendra Prakash', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-raghavendra-prakash', '', '', '2018-03-01 13:13:05', '2018-03-01 13:13:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=383', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(384, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:12', '2017-06-17 07:03:12', 'Dr. Anish Behl is a Consultant Endocrinologist at Apollo BGS Hospitals, Mysore. He has vast experience in treating all kinds of Endocrine disorders and diseases. He is very active as a speaker at numerous Continuing Medical Education (CME) programs, medical conferences, symposia and scientific meetings of the medical community. He is also involved in several clinical trials and research studies.\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n•	Endocrine Disorders.\r\n•	Hormone Disorders\r\n•	Cushing Syndrome\r\n•	Diabetes Management.\r\n•	Gestational Diabetes Management.\r\n•	Insulin Treatment.\r\n•	Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus.\r\n•	Metabolic Bone Diseases.\r\n•	Autoimmune Thyroid Disorders.\r\n•	Hypertension.\r\n', 'Dr. Anish Behl', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-anish-behl', '', '', '2018-03-01 14:06:42', '2018-03-01 14:06:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=384', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
