(347, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:27', '2017-06-17 07:03:27', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine)\r\n\r\nDr. Aftab Ahmed is a Diabetologist in Alwal, Hyderabad and has an experience of 18 years in this field. He completed MBBS from Rangaraya Medical College, Kakinada in 1998 and MD from Andhra Medical College, Visakhapatnam in 2002. He is a member of Indian Medical Association (IMA). Some of the services provided by the doctor are: Adult Diabetes, Childhood Diabetes, Insulin Treatment and Type 1 Diabetes Treatment etc.\r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n 	<li>Type 1 Diabetes.</li>\r\n 	<li>Insulin Management.</li>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes in Children.</li>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes and Infectious Diseases.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Dr. Aftab Ahmed', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-aftab-ahmed', '', '', '2018-03-01 13:51:35', '2018-03-01 13:51:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=347', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(348, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:26', '2017-06-17 07:03:26', 'MBBS, DM (Endocrinology)\r\n\r\nDr. Sridevi Paladugu is an Endocrinologist and practices at Apollo Hospitals in Hyderguda, Hyderabad. She specializes in pediatric endocrinology, thyroid disorders, pituitary disorders, and diabetes mellitus. \r\n\r\nShe provides treatment for:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n        <li>Gestational Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n	<li>Type 1 Diabetes.</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin Management.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypertension.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Pituitary Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Congenital Disorders.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Dr.Sridevi Paladugu', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-sridevi-paladugu', '', '', '2018-03-06 07:36:02', '2018-03-06 07:36:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=348', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(349, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:26', '2017-06-17 07:03:26', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine), FIDM, FEM\r\n\r\nDr. Arshad Punjani is an Internal Medicine and Diabetologist in Hyderguda, Hyderabad and has an experience of 18 years in these fields. He completed MBBS from Dr NTR University of health sciences in 2007 and MD - Internal Medicine from Dr NTR University of health sciences in 2008. Some of the services provided by the doctor are: Thyroid Disorders, Anemia, Asthma Fever, Consultant Physician and General Illness Diabetes etc.\r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n	<li>Type 1 Diabetes.</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin Management.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypertension.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Dr.Arshad Punjani', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-arshad-punjani-2', '', '', '2018-03-01 13:52:36', '2018-03-01 13:52:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=349', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(350, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:26', '2017-06-17 07:03:26', 'Dr. Srinivas S is a Podiatric Surgeon. For a diabetic, the feet are one of the most problem prone areas and not many hospitals have a foot specialist, also known as a podiatrist. Dr. Srinivas is one of the most well-known specialists in the podiatric division.', 'Dr. S.Srinivas', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-s-srinivas', '', '', '2018-03-06 07:16:47', '2018-03-06 07:16:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=350', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(351, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:25', '2017-06-17 07:03:25', 'Dr. Ravi Sankar Erukulapati\r\nMBBS, MRCP (UK), CCT- GIM, Diabetes & Endocrinology (UK)\r\n\r\nDr. Ravi Sankar Erukulapati is a Consultant Endocrinologist and Diabetologist. He practices at Apollo Hospitals in Jubilee Hills, Hyderabad. He is a highly experienced Endocrinologist with special interest in thyroid and other hormone disorders. In his 17 plus-years of practice, he has numerous publications to his credit. He has published papers in several reputed medical journals and societies. Of note, he has also published a book on PLAB 1 exam in UK. His expertise is in providing treatment for both type 1 and type 2 diabetes, and endocrine disorders like obesity, hypogonadism, pituitary disorders, adrenal diseases, gynecomastia, and cancer of the thyroid just to name a few. He has been awarded many gold medals, distinctions, and certificates in his career till now. \r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n•	Diabetes Mellitus, type 1 and type 2.\r\n•	Diabetes Complications including foot ulcers, neuropathy, and peripheral vascular disease.\r\n•	Insulin pump therapy.\r\n•	Continuous Glucose monitoring systems.\r\n•	Lipid Disorders.\r\n•	Diabetes Emergencies.\r\n•	Thyroid Disorders.\r\n•	Pituitary Disorders.\r\n•	Adrenal Disorders.\r\n•	Hypoparathyroidism.\r\n•	Hyperparathyroidism.\r\n•	Hypothyroidism.\r\n•	Hyperthyroidism.\r\n•	Gynecomastia.\r\n•	Delayed Growth.\r\n•	Endocrine Cancers.\r\n•	Thyroid Cancer.\r\n•	Calcium & Bone diseases including osteoporosis, osteomalacia, and vitamin D deficiency.\r\n•	Rare Endocrine Disorders.\r\n•	Endocrine Disorders in critically ill patients.\r\n', 'Dr. Ravi Sankar Erukulapati', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-ravi-sankar-erukulapati', '', '', '2018-03-06 07:33:14', '2018-03-06 07:33:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=351', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
