(353, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:25', '2017-06-17 07:03:25', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine), CDC (AU), PGDD (AU) Diabetology\r\nDr. K. Surya Pavan Reddy is a General Physician & a Diabetologist. He practices at Apollo Hospitals in Jubilee Hills, Hyderabad. He has a vast experience in treating diabetes, diabetes complications, hypertension, and many other conditions.\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 & type 2).</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin Therapy.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Complications.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetic Diet Counseling.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypertension.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypertriglyceridemia.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypercholesterolemia.</li>\r\n\r\n', 'Dr.Surya Pavan Reddy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-surya-pavan-reddy', '', '', '2018-03-06 07:36:29', '2018-03-06 07:36:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=353', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
