(335, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:32', '2017-06-17 07:03:32', 'MBBS, MD (Internal Medicine), DM (Endocrinology), FICP, Fellow of American College of Endocrinology (FACE), FRCP(Lon,Glsg &amp; Edin), FACP(USA)\r\n\r\n<strong>(Padma Shri Awardee, 2014)</strong>\r\n\r\nDr. Shashank R Joshi is an Endocrinologist and Diabetologist who practices at Apollo Sugar Clinics Tardeo, Mumbai and Apollo Spectra Hospitals, Mumbai.\r\nHe is a Padma Shri Award winner in the year 2014 and has won many other awards for his excellence. He has won the International Clinician Award at the 21st American Association of Clinical Endocrinologists Annual Scientific and Clinical Congress.\r\nHe was the former President of the Research Society for the Study of Diabetes in India and All India Association of Advancing Research in Obesity. He was also the former Vice President of the Association of Physicians of India.\r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 and type 2).</li>\r\n 	<li>Insulin therapy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes in Children.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n 	<li>Pituitary Disorders.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cardio-Metabolic Disorders.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Dr Shashank Joshi', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-shashank-joshi', '', '', '2018-03-01 14:01:27', '2018-03-01 14:01:27', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=335', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(337, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:32', '2017-06-17 07:03:32', 'MBBS, DM (Endocrinology)\r\nDr. Tejal Latia is an Endocrinologist who practices at Apollo Sugar Clinics in Belapur, Navi Mumbai. She is a highly experienced endocrinologist with special interest in complicated diabetes, polycystic ovarian disease, and other hormonal conditions.\r\nShe provides treatment for:\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 and type 2).</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin Therapy.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes in Children.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>PCOS.</li>\r\n	<li>Obesity.</li>\r\n	<li>Complicated Diabetes.</li>\r\n	<li>Calcium and Bone Metabolism Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Hormonal and growth disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Cholesterol disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Pituitary disorders.</li>\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Tejal Latia', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-tejal-latia', '', '', '2018-03-01 14:02:58', '2018-03-01 14:02:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=337', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(338, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:31', '2017-06-17 07:03:31', 'MBBS, DNB (Endocrinology, Diabetes, Metabolism) MD (General Medicine)\r\nDr. Mahesh Chavan is a Consultant Endocrinologist at Apollo Sugar Clinics and Apollo Hospitals, Belapur, Navi Mumbai.  He has previously worked in prestigious institutions and has contributed immensely to the department of endocrinology. His special interests metabolic bone diseases, endocrine tumors, and thyroid disorders. He has published several research papers on hyperthyroidism, cardiac metastasis in thyroid carcinoma and many others.\r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 and type 2).</li>\r\n	<li>Endocrine Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Pituitary Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Pediatric Endocrinology.</li>\r\n	<li>Delayed Growth/Puberty.</li>\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Mahesh Chavan', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-mahesh-chavan', '', '', '2018-03-01 13:59:13', '2018-03-01 13:59:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=338', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
(339, 1, '2017-06-17 07:03:31', '2017-06-17 07:03:31', 'He is also practicing as Consultant Diabetologist at the MGM &amp; Fortis Hospitals, Navi Mumbai. He was earlier a Consultant Physician at the Sir Ganga Ram Hospital, Delhi. He is Unit Head &amp; Senior Professor in Post Grad Dept of Internal Medicine &amp; In charge Division of Diabetology at MGM Institute of Health Sciences, which is a 1000 bedded Tertiary Health Care Centre in Navi Mumbai. He is also the Head of Diabetes Specialty Clinic, an advanced Centre for Diabetes Care Research at the MGMIHS. He is a Member Academic Council and Core Research Group and has been Chairman Board of Studies at the MGM University of Health Sciences. He is a Guide &amp; Examiner for DNB, MD, PhD in Medicine all over India. He is a National Faculty and Guest Speaker &amp; Chairperson in many conferences including RSSDI &amp; APICON, MAYO ID. Besides he has been invited as Distinguished Speaker in various prestigious International Conferences on Medicine sponsored by World Health Organization &amp; United Nations &amp; BRICS International Forum from time to time in various parts of the World. He has written many Chapters in Medicine Text books.', 'Dr. Sandeep Rai', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dr-sandeep-rai', '', '', '2018-03-01 14:00:09', '2018-03-01 14:00:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost.org/apollosugar-local/?post_type=our_doctors&#038;p=339', 0, 'our_doctors', '', 0),
