(5517, 1, '2018-02-28 12:41:04', '2018-02-28 12:41:04', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine)\r\n\r\nDr. Aftab Ahmed is a Diabetologist in Alwal, Hyderabad and has an experience of 18 years in this field. He completed MBBS from Rangaraya Medical College, Kakinada in 1998 and MD from Andhra Medical College, Visakhapatnam in 2002. He is a member of Indian Medical Association (IMA). Some of the services provided by the doctor are: Adult Diabetes, Childhood Diabetes, Insulin Treatment and Type 1 Diabetes Treatment etc.\r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n 	<li>Type 1 Diabetes.</li>\r\n 	<li>Insulin Management.</li>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes in Children.</li>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes and Infectious Diseases.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Dr. Aftab Ahmed', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '347-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-28 12:41:04', '2018-02-28 12:41:04', '', 347, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/347-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(5518, 1, '2018-02-28 12:50:05', '2018-02-28 12:50:05', 'MBBS, MD (Internal Medicine), DM (Endocrinology)\r\nDr. Prasanna. B is a Consultant Endocrinologist and practices at Apollo Hospitals, Sugar Clinics Secunderabad. He is an expert in providing treatment for diabetes mellitus and numerous other endocrine disorders.\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Endocrine Disorders.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thyroid Disorders</li>\r\n 	<li>Pituitary Disorders.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hypothyroidism.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hyperthyroidism.</li>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 &amp; type 2).</li>\r\n 	<li>Insulin Therapy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes Complications.</li>\r\n 	<li>Diabetes Diet Counseling.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Dr. Prasanna. B', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4452-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-28 12:50:05', '2018-02-28 12:50:05', '', 4452, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/4452-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
