(5564, 1, '2018-03-01 07:13:32', '2018-03-01 07:13:32', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine), DM (Endocrinology)\r\n\r\nDr. Richa Chaturvedi is a Sr. Endocrinologist and Research Investigator at Apollo Clinics (Sector 14). She is an orator and has been felicitated in various conferences. She is also known for her publications in various medical journals including NEJM. \r\n \r\nShe provides treatment for:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 and type 2)</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Endocrine Disorders.</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Endocrine Disorders in Children.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\nHormonal Disorders in Women.</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Obesity.</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Diabetic Foot.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Richa Chaturvedhi', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '369-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-01 07:13:32', '2018-03-01 07:13:32', '', 369, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/369-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
