(5567, 1, '2018-03-01 07:16:06', '2018-03-01 07:16:06', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine), MRCP (Endocrinology)\r\nDr. Mohd Asim Siddiqui practices at Apollo Centre for Obesity, Diabetes and Endocrinology (ACODE) in Indraprastha Apollo Hospitals, New Delhi. He is a Sr. Consultant Endocrinologist. He specializes in the management of diabetes, and endocrine & metabolic disorders.\r\nHe also specializes in type 1 diabetes, especially in the young, gestational diabetes, and Post-transplant & post-metabolic surgery diabetes. He has expertise in other endocrine disorders involving the pituitary, thyroid, adrenal, and pancreas, along with bone, metabolic, lipid, and reproductive disorders.\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 and type 2).</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin Therapy.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Complications.</li>\r\n	<li>Endocrine Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Pituitary Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Bone and Metabolic Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Adrenal Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Hyperlipidemia.</li>\r\n	<li>Reproductive Disorders. </li>\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Mohammad Asim Siddiqui', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '371-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-01 07:16:06', '2018-03-01 07:16:06', '', 371, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/371-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
