(5569, 1, '2018-03-01 07:18:21', '2018-03-01 07:18:21', 'MBBS, DM (Endocrinology)\r\n\r\nDr. Sambit Das is an Endocrinologist & General Physician and practices at Apollo Hospitals in Gajapati Nagar, Bhubaneswar. He has an illustrious career with numerous awards consisting of Chief Minister’s Merit Award, Gold Medal in Microbiology, and many others.\r\n\r\nHe has published numerous research papers on insulin therapy, Goitre, hyperthyroidism, subacute thyroiditis, and many other topics. He has vast teaching experience as a Professor at Apollo Health Education and Research Foundation Medvarsity, Certificate Course for Evidence-Based Diabetes Management and a course on Thyroid Ultrasound.  \r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Management.</li>\r\n	<li>Type 1 Diabetes.</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin therapy.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Hypothyroidism.</li>\r\n	<li>Hyperthyroidism.</li>\r\n	<li>Pituitary Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Pediatric Endocrine Disorders.</li>\r\n	<li>Thyroid Ultrasound.</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Sambit Das', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '375-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-01 07:18:21', '2018-03-01 07:18:21', '', 375, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/375-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
