(5571, 1, '2018-03-01 07:20:41', '2018-03-01 07:20:41', 'Dr. Dwarakanath C.S. is a highly skilled doctor, having many years of experience in Endocriology. He has worked in many reputed hospitals of Bangalore and has over the years gained fame in this field. He is adept in Endocrinology and treats diabetes and related ailments. He has undergone GCP training in Investigator meetings. He has also participated in one Phase 3 trial in Type 2 Diabetes.', 'Dr. Dwarakanath C.S', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '377-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-01 07:20:41', '2018-03-01 07:20:41', '', 377, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/377-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(5572, 1, '2018-03-01 07:21:59', '2018-03-01 07:21:59', 'MBBS, Diploma in Otorhinolaryngology (DLO), MD (General Medicine) \r\nDr. Arun R Vadavi is a General Physician & a Diabetologist. He practices at Apollo Hospitals in Bannerghatta Road, Bangalore. He has been involved in various training activities and has been a trainer at the Johns Hopkins Academy and American Academy of CME for certified courses in India. He is a post graduate teacher in Diabetology at the Rajiv Gandhi Health University. \r\nHe provides treatment for:\r\n	<li>Diabetes Mellitus (type 1 and type 2).</li>\r\n	<li>Insulin therapy.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Complications.</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetes Diet.</li>\r\n	<li>Cardiology.</li>\r\n	<li>Gestational Diabetes.</li>\r\n\r\n', 'Dr. Arun R Vadavi', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '378-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-01 07:21:59', '2018-03-01 07:21:59', '', 378, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/378-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
