(5574, 1, '2018-03-01 07:24:17', '2018-03-01 07:24:17', 'MBBS, MD (General Medicine), DM (Endocrinology)\r\nDr. Narendra B S, a Consultant Endocrinologist & Diabetologist, practices at Apollo Hospitals in Seshadripuram, Bangalore. \r\n\r\nHe provides treatment for: \r\n\r\n•	Diabetes.\r\n•	Type 1 Diabetes.\r\n•	Gestational Diabetes.\r\n•	Thyroid Disorders.\r\n•	Polycystic Ovarian Syndrome (PCOS).\r\n•	Pituitary/Adrenal Gland Disorders.\r\n•	Growth Disorders.\r\n•	HRT & Hormonal Disorders.\r\n•	Obesity.\r\n•	Menopause.\r\n•	Hirsutism.\r\n•	Erectile Dysfunction.\r\n', 'Dr. Narendra B S', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '381-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-01 07:24:17', '2018-03-01 07:24:17', '', 381, 'http://apollodiabetescare.com/staging/uncategorized/381-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
